# M6 — Weapon pickups render the atlas sprite (variant = WeaponId)
# instead of the kind-colored circle. Other kinds keep the circle.
#
# Reactor's pillar-base has PLASMA_SMG (weapon) at x=1600 and
# HEALTH_SMALL (circle) at x=1280. Spawn between them; aim flat so
# camera lookahead stays horizontal.

window 1280 720
seed 1 1
out build/shots/m6_pickup_weapon_sprite
map reactor

# Standing flat between HEALTH and PLASMA_SMG.
spawn_at 1440 1176
aim 2000 1176

# Three frames across the bob cycle so reviewers see the sprite at
# multiple vertical offsets and confirm bob still drives the new path.
at 30 shot bob_phase_a
at 60 shot bob_phase_b
at 90 shot bob_phase_c

contact_sheet contact cols 3 cell 1280 720

at 120 end
